# Cloudflare Pages redirects. https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/

# Storybook is a raw static bundle at /storybook/ that references its assets
# relatively (./sb-manager/…). Visited without the trailing slash, those
# relative URLs resolve against / and 404, leaving the manager stuck on its
# loading spinner. Force the trailing slash so the manager + preview resolve.
/storybook /storybook/ 301
